{"tid":642893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「沙拿崛起」球王侯補！金球獎賠率沙拿熱過美斯","createTime":"2018-04-26T06:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T12:35:51.000Z","uid":5006,"like":469,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"52b2007776e0de3bbadc92caa037b61526a3ddd4","tid":642893,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180426/photo/bkn-20180426114811634-0426_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180426115618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180426%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180426114811634-0426_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180426115618&h=de74224c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利物浦喺歐聯4強首回合主場以5:2打沉羅馬後，穆罕默德沙拿嘅人氣進一步上升，根據博彩公司最新賠率，沙拿奪得金球獎嘅賠率熱到得3.75倍，比起巴塞隆拿球王美斯嘅6倍更加被睇好，僅次於皇家馬德里巨星C朗嘅3.63倍，報道仲話，假如紅軍同皇馬分別躋身歐聯決賽，到時邊隊贏，就會決定金球獎邊個拎呀！ <br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180426/mobile/bkn-20180426114811634-0426_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180426%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180426114811634-0426_00882_001.html&d=pbNqoPxElrtkwPc8XrrD%2BGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c95d205c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180426/mobile/bkn-20180426114811634-0426_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咩話！拎左雙冠既球王美斯得6倍賠率？！仲要低過連英超都拎唔到既埃及美斯！你叫班小花fans情何以堪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  撐沙拿，可以帶住紅軍崛起值得敬佩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撐美斯，雙冠勁過你啦，歐聯唔太重要姐"},{"pid":"af50d5823cee9db4cfc8dde25001a805925979eb","tid":642893,"uid":5006,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"可能美斯拎埋世界盃呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54211596b516a43a027e1171c4ba757bf0535669","tid":642893,"uid":71433,"like":64,"dislike":55,"score":9,"cited